The,Mobile,Commons,platform,integrates,SMS,phone,calls,and,Web,applications,with,CRMs,and,databases,as,well,as,Twitter,Facebook,applications,flash,widgets,and,geo,location,features,Using,mData,users,can,build,interactive,applications,that,processes,and,respond,to,incoming,SMS,messages,Users,specify,a,URL,and,Mobile,Commons,will,respond,with,an,HTTP,POST,If,a,response,is,specified,in,XML,it,ll,be,formatted,for,mobile